text: Unfinished Story () is a 1955 Soviet drama movie directed by Fridrikh Ermler.Первая леди петербургской сцены Алиса Фрейндлих отмечает юбилейНЕОКОНЧЕННАЯ ПОВЕСТЬ It stars Elina Bystritskaya, Sergey Bondarchuk, and Sofia Giatsintova. == Actors == * Elina Bystritskaya as Yelizaveta Muromtseva * Sergey Bondarchuk as Yuri Yershov * Sofia Giatsintova as Anna Yershova, Yuri's Mother * Yevgeny Samoylov as Aleksandr Aganin * Yevgeni Lebedev as Fyodor Ivanovich == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet movies Category:1955 movies Category:Soviet drama movies
